description:
More Than, Less Than (Little World Math Concepts) 
Author: Joanne Mattern 




Little World Math Concepts is a new sereies that explores early math concepts, such as Left or Right, by providing young children with a clear definition of the concept and when several real-world examples of the concept. The bright photographs keep kids engaged as they develop math skills. 


Genre: Childrens | Non Fiction
